# Cascade-truncation: when dot-np-directory fails, 13 downstream checks are
# skipped. agent-instructions passes (CLAUDE.md present) and git-ignore is
# NotApplicable (no .git). The trailing summary must read:
#   "2 of 16 checks ran, 1 finding (1 error). 13 checks skipped (cascade prerequisite failed)."
# Parens in regex assertions must be escaped.

! exec np admin doctor
stdout '2 of 16 checks ran, 1 finding \(1 error\). 13 checks skipped \(cascade prerequisite failed\).'

-- CLAUDE.md --
Use np to manage issues. Run `np agent prime` for setup.
